  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety, tolerability, and efficacy of AEB071 as a
      therapy for uveitis. Vision improvement and reduction in the swelling of retina will be
      measured for the assessment of efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
